        "## Load Maize Price Data\n",
        "\n",
        "Let's load and process the price data for 'Maiz' (corn) from the `SeriesTiempoMaiz.xlsx` file. This will create a separate dataset for maize prices."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
          "height": 431
        },
        "id": "15ec6a27",
